"{{{ Backup, swap and undo files
"------------------------ Backup, swap and undo files -------------------------

" Making sure directories into which we are going to save backup, swap and undo
" files exist (directory for those files is '~/.cache/nvim/'). If they don't
" exist, they will be created.
